{
  "texts": [
    "The Japan Society of Radiological Technology has generated a dataset for lung nodule image classification (http:// imgcom. jsrt.",
    "jp/ minij srtdb/) [56].The NLST CT scan image collection, which comprises over 200,000 image series from 75,000 CT tests, was compiled by more than 25,000 individuals.",
    "The cancer data access system (CDAS) provided access to a subset of lung cancer images that contained around 28,000 images from approximately 3,700 individuals (https:// cdas. cancer.",
    "gov/ learn/ nlst/ images/) [65].",
    "Four hundred twenty-two individuals with NSCLC are featured [72]."
  ]
}